These unidentified '''Rutian septuplets''' were a group of seven turquoise-skinned [[Rutian/Legends|Rutian]] [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'leks]] who were en route' to the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim Territories]] to be given to a [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]]. However, before they could be successfully delivered, their "[[Transport/Legends|transport]]" was hijacked and they were taken by [[Krayn]]. He later sold them as [[Slavery/Legends|slaves]] to the [[Brodogon Consortium]].

